column5: Thanks for your help today with my motor troubles, I appreciate the time you both took.   It must have been fun to watch such a stubborn person not give up untill it was well past obvious that it was not gonna happen.   I hope this is not a sign of how my season is gonna go.... PS the skunk is still strong *sigh*

No worries at all, thats one of the reasons we are here... to hand out tools and of course giggle a little when we see someone like you keep their sense of humour when things just do not go right.  Atleast you got out and gave it your best shot!  See you again soon, hopefully everything will go smoothly for you next time!  Cheers  Jen
